Today, I handed out a lot of flyers, door-to-door stickers, urging people not to go out.
之前还觉得这次疫情和普通流感差不多，但最近感觉变严重了。
It was previously thought to be about the same as ordinary flu, but it has been feeling worse lately.
突然想起去年12月有亲戚从武汉回来，她陪孩子在武汉读书，那个时候大家都还不知道这个疫情。
Suddenly remembered last December when a relative returned from Wuhan, she accompanied her children in Wuhan, when everyone did not know the epidemic.
今天打了电话，幸亏他们现在还都挺好的，目前还没有发热的情况。
Today, I called and luckily they are all fine now. There is no fever at the moment.
更多没有防备的人被感染，然后被确诊送院治疗。
More unguarded people are infected and are then diagnosed for treatment.
一位感染了新冠肺炎的女儿从武汉回黄冈娘家为病逝的母亲奔丧，不幸将一家10名亲友都感染了。
A daughter infected with pneumonia returned to her mother's home in Huanggang from Wuhan to mourn her mother's death, tragically infecting 10 family members.
【梦轩：治愈新冠肺炎患者】1月21日住院第三天，我哥哥从深圳赶回来了。
Futagami: Healing the Patients With New Crown Pneumonia On January 21, my brother returned from Shenzhen for the third day of hospitalization.
我哥当时就站在病房窗外迟迟不肯离开，他眼泪在打转，我知道他担心我。
My brother was standing outside the ward window, his tears twirling. I knew he was worried about me.
他也不害怕传染，一日三餐都给我送饭，有热腾腾的肉汤，也有青菜和米饭。
He was not afraid of infection. He gave me three meals a day, hot broth, vegetables and rice.
当时医院里也有病号伙食，尽管不是很好。
There was sick food in the hospital, too, though not very well.
其实那时候到处封路，送饭会被劝阻，真的很不容易，我也很感动。
In fact, at that time everywhere blocked the road, the delivery of food will be discouraged, really not easy, I am also very moved.
我怕哥哥担心，坚持每天跟他汇报病情，比如说“今天比昨天好多了，请你们放心”这样的话，其实也是在鼓励自己要有信心，一定要挺过来！那段日子里，我的好朋友偶尔也会送来鸡汤，每天从早到晚发消息关心我的病情，鼓励我挺下去。
I am afraid my brother is worried and I insist on reporting my illness to him every day, such as "Today is much better than yesterday, please rest assured." In those days, my good friends occasionally send chicken soup, from morning to night to care about my illness and encourage me to stay there.
如果有消息说什么药物对治疗“新冠肺炎”有帮助，朋友们都会想方设法帮弄到，送过来。
If there's any news that drugs might be helpful in treating New Crown Pneumonia, friends will try to get it and deliver it.
后面，我坚决拒绝了哥哥和其他朋友的送汤送饭。
Later, I firmly rejected my brother and other friends to send soup and food.
来往医院或者在路上，都有暴露被感染的风险。
There is a risk of exposure to infection both during travel to and from hospitals and on the road.
我怕他们因我而感染，那我无论如何过意不去。
I'm afraid they're infected with me, and I'm sorry anyway.
1月22日从19日我住进病房开始，医院不断收治到新的病患。
January 22nd From the day I was admitted to the ward on January 19th, the hospital kept receiving new patients.
每个病房四五个床位，听医生说，医院很快就要住满了。
Four or five beds in each ward, according to the doctor, the hospital will soon be full.
我们病房4张床位很快满员。
Four beds in our ward soon filled up.
邻床病友是一位40岁多岁的武汉人，娘家在黄冈。
Next to the bed patient is a 40-year-old Wuhan, her family in Huanggang.
前一阵子她因年老的妈妈去世回家奔丧，之前就有类似感冒症状，办完丧事她也被确诊“新冠肺炎”，送医隔离治疗。
Some time ago she came home from the death of her old mother with flu-like symptoms. She was diagnosed with New Crown Pneumonia and treated in isolation.
不幸地是，她娘家十个人估计都被感染，陆续全被确诊送医。
Unfortunately, ten members of her mother's family are believed to have been infected and are being treated.
在病房里，这位病友因为病痛，也因为心理压力大，每天哭泣。
In the ward, the sick man cried every day because of illness and psychological stress.
据她说，不少亲友都在责怪埋怨她。
According to her, many friends and relatives are blaming her.
另外两位病友，大概都在50岁左右，都是黄冈人。
The other two patients, both about 50 years old, were all Huanggang people.
一个是家庭主妇，平常喜欢呼朋聚友打麻将，另外一位经常走村串门做“法事”。
One is a housewife, usually like to play Mahjong Hupung friends, another often go to the village to do "law."
如何感染上“新冠病毒”，她们自己都有些说不清楚。
How to get infected with the new crown virus is not clear to them.
初入医院的几天，治疗护理等有不到位的地方，连医护自身都没办法做好防护。
The first few days into the hospital, treatment and care, such as places not in place, even the medical themselves can not do a good job of protection.
医生、护士戴着普通的一次性医用口罩、眼罩，白大褂外面套一件长风衣似的一次性防护服。
Doctors and nurses wear ordinary disposable medical masks, eye masks, white coats and a long windbreaker-like disposable protective clothing.
病人太多，打针换药的频率很高，医护进入病房的频率却并不高。
There are too many patients, the frequency of needle exchange is very high, the frequency of medical care into the ward is not high.
有时候输液盐水完了，病人按铃几次护士才能进来。
Sometimes when the infusion brine has run out, the patient rings the bell several times before the nurse enters.
我其实很理解：面对新冠肺炎这种高传染疾病，在这种简陋的防护条件下，医生护士也是胆战心惊的，谁能不怕死呢！住院开始的几天，医院并没有得到新冠肺炎免费治疗的政策。
I really understand that doctors and nurses are terrified of the possibility of dying under these rudimentary protective conditions in the face of a highly contagious disease like Newcastle Pneumonia, a hospital that did not receive free treatment for pneumonia in the first few days of hospitalization.
病人的治疗，除了医保报销项目，其他都需要病人自费。
The patient's treatment, with the exception of Medicare reimbursement, requires the patient to pay his or her own expenses.
【金昊：治愈新冠肺炎患者】1月21日这一天，我在朋友圈看到有个朋友已经确诊感染了“新冠肺炎”。
