于是，妈妈把我家银行卡的密码一个个告诉我，还安慰我说“哭出来好点，哭出来就舒服了”。
So my mother told me the password of my bank card one by one, and comforted me by saying, "Cry out better, cry out to be comfortable."
我也不是想哭，就是情难自禁。
I either want to cry or I can't help myself.
哎！都这时候了，我们一家人得做好打一场硬仗的准备了。
Well, it's time for our family to get ready for a hard fight.
