"I replied," Hmm.
”麻城市人民医院发热门诊附近的导引牌1月23日早上七点一到，我和妈妈便从床上爬了起来。
My mother and I climbed out of bed on January 23, at seven o'clock in the morning, near the fever clinic at Massachusetts People's Hospital.
昨天爸爸突然被隔离治疗，没有带任何东西，今天我们也要去医院给他送洗漱用品。
Yesterday my father was treated in isolation, without anything with him, and today we are going to the hospital to bring him toiletries.
早上的医院还很安静，大家都带着口罩，除了呼呼吹来的风，只有阵阵咳嗽声传来。
The morning hospital was quiet, with everyone wearing masks and coughing except for the blowing wind.
我们先去的感染科住院部，此时医院已经用隔离带划分好了各种区域，除了住院病人，只有送东西的人可以跨过感染科前面的这条隔离带。
We went first to the Infection Department, where the hospital had already zoned out various areas, except for inpatients, where only the courier could cross the isolation strip in front of the infection section.
感染科的伸缩门被一把大锁锁着，我们需要先给爸爸打电话，爸爸再按铃叫护士，护士下来代领东西，这中间颇要一段时间。
The infection department's telescopic door was locked by a big lock. We needed to call Dad first. Dad rang the bell for the nurse, and the nurse came down to pick it up.
我们也遇见了同样戴口罩来送东西的两个人。
We also met two men wearing masks to deliver things.
我很想问问别人家的情况，但妈妈瞟了我一眼，示意我不要多说话，我便也不好再出声了。
I wanted to ask someone what was going on at home, but my mother glanced at me and motioned me not to talk more.
护士终于下来了，向我们确认好床号和病人姓名这才开门把东西拿进去，还一脸严肃地叮嘱我们：“你们家人送东西要一次送齐，不要一直往这跑，这里不是什么好地方，我们也很忙。
The nurse finally came down, confirmed the bed number and the patient's name, opened the door, took the things in, and said to us gravely, "Your family needs to send things all at once, not all the way here.
”我们只得应着，看来不仅是我们，医院的护士也很紧张吧。
"We had to respond, and it seemed that not only we, but also the nurses at the hospital, were nervous.
接下来，我和妈妈去门诊登记信息，然后量体温、挂号，等上三五分钟凑齐五六个人，护士便会把我们一起带到发热门诊，我们再在这里等待叫号。
Next, my mother and I went to the clinic to check in the information, then took my temperature, registered, and waited three or five minutes for five or six people, and the nurse would take us to the fever clinic, where we would wait for a call.
发热门诊在单独的一小栋房子里，进门是一条大概两人宽、三五米长的小道，护士便在这里收大家的挂号条。
The Heat Clinic is in a small separate house. Inside it is a path about two people wide and three or five meters long.
更多的人为了避免交叉感染，还是选择等在外面。
More people choose to wait outside in order to avoid cross-infection.
这里咳嗽的人更多一些。
There are more people coughing here.
我和妈妈早上来，一直到中午才轮到我们看病。
My mother and I came in the morning and it wasn't our turn to see the doctor until noon.
医生问诊完，便是去做血常规和CT，血常规大概半个小时可以拿结果，CT应该是等到了下午三四点。
After the doctor's consultation, is to do blood routine and CT, blood routine about half an hour can get the results, CT should wait until 3 or 4 pm.
我稍稍看了下CT报告单，我妈应该是只有支气管炎，而我应该是肺部有炎症了。
I took a look at the CT report. My mom was supposed to have bronchitis, and I was supposed to have inflammation in my lungs.
果然，医生先看完我妈的片子再看我的，问了句：“你妈没有感染，你怎么被感染了呢？”听到这句话，我应该是有点歉意的笑了笑。
Sure enough, the doctor watched my mom's film before seeing mine and asked, "How did you get infected when your mother wasn't infected?" I should have smiled apologetically.
我想没有办法了，我已经被感染了，只有接受了。
I don't think I can help it. I'm infected. I just have to accept it.
CT片子显示，我双肺下叶少许感染。
CT scans showed a slight infection in my lower lobe.
医生建议早治疗，但也不强制我住院，甚至还微笑地推荐我去给对面那位医生看看，对面医生是感染科专家。
The doctor advised early treatment, but did not force me to go to the hospital. He even smiled and recommended me to see the doctor across the street, who was an infection specialist.
医生说，如果要住院的话，我就得直接办理住院手续。
The doctor said that if I had to be hospitalized, I would have to go straight to the hospital.
我有点害怕，但是万一真的是这个病，我不住院回去也是祸害人。
I'm a little scared, but if it's really the disease, it's a scourge if I don't go back to the hospital.
纠结再三，我办了住院手续。
After many problems, I went to the hospital.
因为到处都有隔离带限制，妈妈不能送我过去，我便只有硬着头皮往前走了，可是却被告知感染科里已经住满了，如果再进人，就必须两人一间，我不愿意冒这个险，与医生协商后，决定回家住一晚，第二天麻城就有试剂盒了，我直接来做试剂盒检查。
As there were restrictions on the quarantine zone everywhere, my mother could not see me through, so I had to go ahead hard, but was told that the infective unit was full, and if anyone else came in, I would not risk it.
这晚下起蒙蒙细雨，我带着帽子等着已经回家的妈妈来接我。
It was a drizzling night, and I was waiting for my mother, who had come home, to pick me up with my hat.
我只想着，今天我终于还是回了家，我答应妈妈的事我做到了。
I just thought, today I finally returned home, I promised my mother I did.
（文中梦轩、叶薇为化名）【未完待续】(本文来自澎湃新闻，更多原创资讯请下载“澎湃新闻”APP)。
